    verification indicatorTypeStandupGate : Test { :>> id = "63940516-2c7d-4e8f-b092-51627384bd06"; :>> title = "Sprint 92 standup gate"; :>> createdAt = "2026-06-22"; :>> createdBy = "claudeOpus"; :>> method = VerificationMethod::inspect; :>> procedureText = "Approach: schema/core/indicator.sysml (Indicator/Measurement + 2 enums) + _schema_files SCHEMA_ORDER + _ID_TYPES; view.rs indicators/indicator_status/measurement_series (reuse headline_at/trend_series for computed); write.rs append_measurement (#Measures); main.rs cmd_indicators + cmd_record_measurement; process + skill + registry + viewpoint; instances for all 3 methods; D0089 + critiques + doc-sync. Watch: 'at' is a reserved keyword (use measuredAt); bare `dependency` isn't ingested (use #Measures/#Informs markers); add 'indicators' to VIEW_SUBCOMMANDS. No blockers."; }
